								/></a>
							</div>
							<div class="col-lg-6">
								<h2 class="card-title">
									Homelessness in South Africa
								</h2>
								<p class="card-text">
									Homelessness in South Africa is mostly
									caused by a severe housing shortage, 28
									percent unemployment, and urbanization (CIA,
									2017). In 2015, there were 200,000 homeless
									individuals on the streets alone, and
									tremendous inequality prevailed, with around
									79 percent of the population living in
									poverty (DW, 2019).
								</p>
								<a
									class="btn btn-primary"
									href="http://www.scielo.org.za/pdf/hts/v76n1/04.pdf"
								>
									Read More
								</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card mb-4">
					<div class="card-body">
