								/></a>
							</div>
							<div class="col-lg-6">
								<h2 class="card-title">
									It Can Happen To Anyone
								</h2>
								<p class="card-text">
									The phenomenon of street homelessness is
									multifaceted and resists simple
									classifications (De Beer 2015:2; Roets et
									al. 2016:624; Sanchez 2010:102; Somerville
									2013:384). Street homelessness is a visible
									representation of being without shelter, and
									it can take many forms (Naidoo 2010:129).
								</p>
								<a
